snippet.textDisplay: Many people think that this is a song about 2 lovers but actually it is Faiz showing love for his country. He says that, you(beloved) are still beautiful and charming but there are some loves greater than the love of a woman. Like the love for one's country. Seeing and remembering all the blood soaked corpses and their desolate condition in the sand has made him (Faiz) remember his love for his country. And repeatedly asks his lover to not expect the same love from him as in the past because he has found a far greater love. Love for his nation, country and motherland.
